-- Aflac Hires Lebish as Operating Chief for Group Coverage in U.S.
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 2013-08-19T14:12:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-19/aflac-hires-lebish-as-operating-chief-for-group-coverage-in-u-s-.html
Aflac Inc., the largest provider of
supplemental health insurance, hired Daniel Lebish to the newly
created position of chief operating officer of the unit
providing group coverage in the U.S.  Lebish joins from Highmark Blue Cross Blue Shield and will
be based in Columbia, South Carolina, according to a PR Newswire
statement today from Columbus, Georgia-based Aflac.  To contact the reporter on this story:
